{"title":"WACC and Project Evaluation","markdown":{"headingText":"WACC and Project Evaluation","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n```{r}\n#| eval: true\n#| results: asis\n#| echo: false\n#| warning: false\nrf <- rnorm(1, mean = 0.04, sd = 0.005)\nmrp <- rnorm(1, mean = 0.06, sd = 0.005)\nbeta_proj <- rnorm(1, mean = 1.1, sd = 0.1)\nrd <- rnorm(1, mean = 0.05, sd = 0.005)\nde_ratio <- rnorm(1, mean = 0.8, sd = 0.2)\ntax <- rnorm(1, mean = 0.3, sd = 0.02)\n```\n\nA new division of Aurora Technologies is being valued.  \n- Project beta = **`r round(beta_proj,2)`**  \n- Risk-free rate = **`r round(rf*100,2)`**%  \n- Market risk premium = **`r round(mrp*100,2)`**%  \n- Cost of debt = **`r round(rd*100,2)`**%  \n- Debt-to-equity ratio = **`r round(de_ratio,2)`**  \n- Corporate tax rate = **`r round(tax*100,2)`**%  \n\n::: {.question-block}\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 6px;\">\n  <label for=\"module4_num_q7a\"><strong>1. What is the cost of equity capital (in %)?</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module4_num_q7a\" name=\"module4_num_q7a\" style=\"width: 150px;\"\n         data-correct-answer=`r round((rf + beta_proj*mrp)*100,2)` data-tolerance=\"0.01\" />\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module4_num_q7a\" class=\"feedback\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ Cost of Equity = r<sub>f</sub> + β × MRP = **`r round((rf + beta_proj*mrp)*100,2)`**%.  \nThis reflects shareholders’ required return for the project’s systematic risk.\n</div>\n:::\n\n::: {.question-block}\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 6px;\">\n  <label for=\"module4_num_q7b\"><strong>2. What is the WACC (in %)?</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module4_num_q7b\" name=\"module4_num_q7b\" style=\"width: 150px;\"\n         data-correct-answer=`r round(((1/(1+de_ratio))*(rf+beta_proj*mrp) + (de_ratio/(1+de_ratio))*rd*(1-tax))*100,2)` data-tolerance=\"0.01\" />\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module4_num_q7b\" class=\"feedback\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ WACC = (E/V)×r<sub>E</sub> + (D/V)×r<sub>D</sub>×(1–tax) = **`r round(((1/(1+de_ratio))*(rf+beta_proj*mrp) + (de_ratio/(1+de_ratio))*rd*(1-tax))*100,2)`**%.  \nThis is the appropriate discount rate for valuing projects of similar risk.\n</div>\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["../../../../include/webex.css"],"include-after-body":["../../../../include/webex.js"],"output-file":"module4_num_q7 (1).html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"